data.title: Instagram Queen of the Week: Sanaya Irani
data.meta_description: Sanaya recently made her debut on Insta and she has already crossed 200K followers. Also seeing her fans on Instagram, Instagram became her lover too.
data.text:
Sanaya Irani who started her career from a small screen show has become the internet sensation as the Instagram queen of the week. A person who was not so social to become an Instagram queen is the most happiest thing. The most gorgeous girl is the Instagram queen. Sanaya Irani is a woman of multiple talents and loves to dance. She is the cutest person born. It is her fan followers and us people who made her the Instagram queen of the week.

Sayana Irani is really worth of it. You can go and check down her Instagram feed she has updates of what so ever so do and rocks with her gorgeous beauty in each and every post and video of her. Talking about her recent Instagram, she has 2M Followers on Instagram which tells us about how much fans she owns and loved by the audience either by her beauty or her talent. Sanaya Irani had a love for a modelling career and she did it for two years 2005-07. Irani’s first modelling portfolio was done by photographer-turned actor Boman Irani. She is the only Indian television actress to be listed in People Magazine’s (India) forty most beautiful women. Irani has received three ‘Face of The Year’ awards and was the only television actress to be included in People Magazine (India)’s forty most beautiful women.

She was titled the 3rd Attractive Asian Woman Alive. Established actress (2011-14)Sanaya Irani became popular in the youth based show,’ Miley Jab Hum Tum’. And in past she was playing the role of Khushi Kumari Gupta in Star Plus’ Iss Pyaar Ko Kya Naam Doon?. Irani was a finalist for the eight seasons of Jhalak Dikhhla Jaa. She later participated in Nach Baliye in 2017 with her partner Mohit Sehgal and won the third place.
